        <mxCell id="note2" value="&lt;b&gt;ComponentGuard ACCESS_LEVELS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;PUBLIC&lt;/b&gt; — no auth required&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;AUTHENTICATED&lt;/b&gt; — valid session required&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;OWNER_ONLY&lt;/b&gt; — role = owner + admin-level permission&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;PERMISSION_BASED&lt;/b&gt; — role intersection check vs MODULE_PERMISSIONS[]" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#b85450;fillColor=#f8cecc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=10;rounded=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="560" y="395" width="400" height="130" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="note3" value="&lt;b&gt;HMAC-SHA256 Session Signing:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1. Login succeeds &amp;rarr; BFF has { employee, tokens, permissions }&lt;br/&gt;2. SessionManager.signMeta(payload, AUTH_SECRET) &amp;rarr; compact JWS&lt;br/&gt;3. JWS stored as __hris_meta cookie (httpOnly, server-set only)&lt;br/&gt;4. On GET /api/auth/token &amp;rarr; verifyMeta(cookie, AUTH_SECRET)&lt;br/&gt;5. Failure &amp;rarr; 401, cookies untouched&lt;br/&gt;6. AUTH_SECRET server-only — Web Crypto API, Edge-compatible" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#82b366;fillColor=#d5e8d4;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=10;rounded=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="560" y="545" width="400" height="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
